
New Features in clog 1.3.0

  - The 'suppress' action now suppresses the newline also.
  - Overlapping matches are properly handled. There is now no limit to the
    number of colored elements on a line.

  Please refer to the ChangeLog file for full details.

---

Clog has been built and tested on the following configurations:

  * OS X
  * Fedora
  * Ubuntu
  * Debian
  * Arch
  * FreeBSD
  * Cygwin

---

While Clog has undergone testing, bugs are sure to remain.  If you
encounter a bug, please enter a new issue at:

  https://bug.tasktools.org

Or just send a message to:

  support@taskwarrior.org

Thank you.
